OL,3,CJustice Secretary warns of 'moment of
OL,4,Creckoning' for grooming gangs scandal
OL,6,FThe grooming gangs scandal faces a
OL,7,F"moment of reckoning," the Justice
OL,8,FSecretary has warned ahead of the
OL,9,Fpublication of a national report on
OL,10,Fchild sexual exploitation.
OL,12,FShabana Mahmood said there was a need
OL,13,Ffor "truth and reconciliation" for
OL,14,Fpeople whose trust in authorities had
OL,15,Fbeen "fundamentally shaken, if not
OL,16,Ftotally broken".
