OL,3,CJustice Secretary warns of 'moment of
OL,4,Creckoning' for grooming gangs scandal
OL,6,FA "rapid" audit, led by Baroness
OL,7,FLouise Casey and looking at the scale
OL,8,Fof grooming gangs across England and
OL,9,FWales, had been expected to report
OL,10,Fback after Easter.
OL,12,FDowning Street has said the process is
OL,13,Fconcluding this month and the findings
OL,14,Fwill be published in "due course".
OL,16,FIn an interview with the Spectator
OL,17,Fmagazine, Ms Mahmood said that there
OL,18,Fhad been a number of successful
OL,19,Fprosecutions against criminals
OL,20,Finvolved in the scandal.
