OL,3,CJustice Secretary warns of 'moment of
OL,4,Creckoning' for grooming gangs scandal
OL,6,F"But the way that this scandal has
OL,7,Fplayed out asks a bigger question,
OL,8,Fwhich is that you might be getting
OL,9,Faccountability and justice through the
OL,10,Fcriminal justice system, (but) it
OL,11,Fdoesn't feel like proper
OL,12,Faccountability and justice for all of
OL,13,Fthe victims," she said.
OL,15,F"And that's because there is still
OL,16,F(an) outstanding question of why so
OL,17,Fmany people maybe looked the other
OL,18,Fway, or why this wasn't picked up and
OL,19,Fgiven the prominence that was needed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@MO]wD@AOU
