OL,3,CJustice Secretary warns of 'moment of
OL,4,Creckoning' for grooming gangs scandal
OL,6,F"And so that's why justice might
OL,7,Ftechnically have been delivered. But
OL,8,Fthere's still a moment of reckoning to
OL,9,Fcome."
OL,11,FShe added: "Whether local authorities,
OL,12,Fchildren's services, police officers,
OL,13,Fall sorts of people you would feel you
OL,14,Fcan trust, and that trust has been
OL,15,Ffundamentally shaken, if not totally
OL,16,Fbroken, in some of these places."
