OL,3,CJustice Secretary warns of 'moment of
OL,4,Creckoning' for grooming gangs scandal
OL,6,FIt comes after a seven-year national
OL,7,Finquiry led by Professor Alexis Jay,
OL,8,Fwhich found institutional failings and
OL,9,Ftens of thousands of victims across
OL,10,FEngland and Wales.
OL,12,FAs well as the national audit, which
OL,13,Fwill look at the scale, nature and
OL,14,Fprofile of group-based abuse,
OL,15,Fincluding offender characteristics,
OL,16,Fthe Government has also announced
OL,17,Fsupport for five local inquiries in
OL,18,Fareas like Oldham.
